room_title: Escape room "Spy Alley" by Escape Now Houston in Houston
room_description: There is a mole in the Paris field office of the CIA. The CIA has flown you and your team to Paris to figure out who the mole is. To protect the information one of the agents found about the mole, he installed a lockdown in the office. When you enter the field office the door locks behind you. You have 60 minutes to find out who the mole is and escape before the French police arrive to arrest you.
